                <p>School Sentiment does not require user accounts to write reviews or browse the noticeboard. All reviews are posted anonymously. We do not collect usernames or passwords. However, we do collect basic technical data (e.g., IP address, browser type) to prevent abuse and maintain service security, as outlined in our <a href="/privacy" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
