                    <li>Contains spam, viruses, or any form of malicious code.</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-3">We reserve the right to remove any review that violates these guidelines, without notice. Repeated violations may lead to a ban from future submissions (via IP address or email).</p>
            </section>

