                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">4. School Noticeboard Guidelines</h2>
                <p>The School Noticeboard allows users to post items for sale, free items, and wanted ads. When using the noticeboard, you agree to:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
                    <li><strong>Post honest descriptions</strong> - Accurately describe the condition, price, and details of items</li>
                    <li><strong>Upload appropriate photos</strong> - Photos must show the actual item; no inappropriate, offensive, or copyrighted images</li>
                    <li><strong>Not post prohibited items</strong> - Including but not limited to: illegal items, weapons, alcohol, tobacco, prescription medication, or counterfeit goods</li>
                    <li><strong>Complete transactions safely</strong> - Arrange collection in a public place; School Sentiment is not involved in any transactions</li>
                    <li><strong>Respond to messages promptly</strong> - If you are no longer selling an item, mark it as sold or delete the ad</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-3">We reserve the right to remove any ad that violates these guidelines. Repeated violations may lead to account suspension.</p>
            </section>

