            <section>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">6. School Claims & Verification</h2>
                <p>School staff members may claim their school profile to:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
                    <li>Edit school contact information (phone, website, description)</li>
                    <li>Reply to reviews (one reply per review)</li>
                    <li>Display a "Verified School" badge</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-2">To claim a school, you must:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
                    <li>Use a work email address from a .sch.uk or .ac.uk domain (or provide proof of affiliation)</li>
                    <li>Provide your name and role at the school</li>
                    <li>Agree to respond to reviews professionally and constructively</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-2">School replies must be respectful and factual. We reserve the right to remove replies that are defamatory, abusive, or contain personal information.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
